{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_13_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺はなんでも言ってくれ、と言った\n確かに言った、けど……",
      "startTime": 4.2648747228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、いきますよ～！　次は\n『卒業式で生徒に呼び出された先生』でお願いします！",
      "startTime": 11.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "またこういう役回りなのか……\n演技が下手でも笑わないでくれよ",
      "startTime": 18.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。そこは気にしませんから\nとにかくほら、よーい、アクション！",
      "startTime": 25.1072646571,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5976.771836000001,
          "startTime": 31.0840364931
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――前日の夜",
      "startTime": 29.8507035413,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2929.2964587000015,
          "startTime": 32.78
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 30.9907035747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　渚からメッセージだ。「明日、自主練に\n付き合ってくれませんか？」、なるほど。えーっと……",
      "startTime": 36.7666673024,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5986.326169799994,
          "startTime": 42.7529934722
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8266.666666699997,
          "startTime": 45.0333339691
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11115.156824099999,
          "startTime": 47.8818241265
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "「明日なら空いてるから、レッスンルームで\n待ち合わせよう」と。よし",
      "startTime": 46.0000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――練習当日",
      "startTime": 51.007366514,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1292.634121799999,
          "startTime": 52.3000006358
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 52.1473665474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\n来て、くれたんだね……嬉しい",
      "startTime": 55.9333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（あれ？　渚の様子がいつもと違うぞ）\n（……もしかして『自主練』って、演技の練習か？）",
      "startTime": 64.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私、ずっと言いたかったけど、言えなかった\nでも、今日は勇気を出します",
      "startTime": 74.5140550136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "私、{user}さんのことが……\nずっと……！",
      "startTime": 81.9666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（……い、いや、これは本当に演技なのか！？）\n（全然そうは見えないし、万が一にも違ったら……！）",
      "startTime": 87.019189097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待ってくれ、渚\n渚と俺は、アイドルとマネージャーの関係で！",
      "startTime": 94.4000006358,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7776.293553200006,
          "startTime": 102.176294189
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほど～、そういう反応になるんですね\nじゃあ今のを元に、言い回しを調整して……",
      "startTime": 102.3353647553,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4837.81040449999,
          "startTime": 107.1731751598
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　良かった、いつも通りの渚だ\nというか、なぁ、一体何をメモしてるんだ？",
      "startTime": 111.3000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "今度のライブでやる、胸キュン告白選手権のセリフを\n考えているんです。その練習に付き合ってほしくて",
      "startTime": 119.8000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "今のは不意に告白された時、どういうリアクションに\nなるのかどうしても知りたくって、試しちゃいました",
      "startTime": 128.3000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、サニピがやってたあの企画のことか\nそういえばやるって言っていたな、告白の実演企画",
      "startTime": 136.3000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、慌ててる顔、とっても可愛かったですよ\n今の告白どうでした？　きゅんきゅんしてくれました？",
      "startTime": 146.5333360036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "きゅんきゅん……というか、肝が冷えたな……\nまぁ、何をすればいいのかは分かったよ",
      "startTime": 155.5368660279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "つまり俺は、告白の練習相手になればいいんだな\n告白されてどんな風に感じたか、とか伝えたりすれば",
      "startTime": 163.566669337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "それと、{user}さんにも\nメンバーの告白セリフを読んでほしいんです",
      "startTime": 169.8333360036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "他の人に読んでもらわないといまいち感じが掴めなくて\nだからお願いします！",
      "startTime": 178.666669337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "俺はなんでも言ってくれ、と言った\n確かに言った、けど……",
      "startTime": 184.566669337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、いきますよ～！　次は\n『卒業式で生徒に呼び出された先生』でお願いします！",
      "startTime": 191.3000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……今ので十本目か\nどの告白も確かに可愛いけど、サニピの時と随分違うな",
      "startTime": 202.485585453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないですよ～。どれもきゅんってしちゃう\n設定とシチュエーションの、自信作です！",
      "startTime": 210.9189918576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "それだ。サニピの時は\n『さくら達ならどう告白する』って感じだったのに",
      "startTime": 216.366669337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "『幼馴染同士の告白』とか『職場の先輩後輩での告白』\nとか、設定に凝り過ぎて、もし恋みたいだぞ",
      "startTime": 224.7333360036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そこは趣味……じゃなくて。今日練習してみて\nどれくらい設定を盛るか決めようと思ってたんです",
      "startTime": 234.166669337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "次で最後にしますから\n『久しぶりに地元で再会した幼馴染同士』での告白です",
      "startTime": 240.7000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "すぅー……はぁー……\nよし、いつでもいいぞ、渚。来い！",
      "startTime": 252.1000158946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりだね。なんか、君、結構変わったよね\n背も伸びたし、なんていうか……",
      "startTime": 265.6000240326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_02-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、優しいのは昔から変わらないか\nでも、でもね……その……再会したばっかりだけど",
      "startTime": 275.656781584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
